Package: automagic
Type: Package
Title: Automagically Install Required R Packages
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Cole Brokamp
Maintainer: Cole Brokamp <cole.brokamp@gmail.com>
Description: This package parses R code in a given directory for R packages and attempts to install them from CRAN or GitHub. Optionally use a dependencies file for tighter control over which package versions to install. It also contains helper tools for dockerizing an rshiny app and deploying it to an Amazon Web Services Docker Registry.
License: GPL
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.0)
Imports:
    knitr,
    formatR,
    pacman,
    githubinstall,
    dplyr,
    purrr,
    devtools,
    packrat
URL: https://github.com/cole-brokamp/automagic
BugReports: https://github.com/cole-brokamp/automagic/issues
